MBOMBELA &#8211; A man has died after an Asbestos pipe fell on top of him today. According to Netcare911 spokesman Ms Athlenda Mathe, the incident occurred at a site on the R37 about 20 kilometers outside the city. &#8220;The exact detail to the cause of the incident will remain a subject for police investigation and comment,&#8221; she said. Netcare911 paramedics worked alongside paramedics from another emergency service on scene. When the paramedics arrived at the scene, they found the man had already succumbed to his injuries. He was declared dead on the scene.